decks.notes: The main focus of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with a swarm of artifact creatures and Thopter tokens generated by Sai, Master Thopterist. The deck aims to control the board with cards like Ensnaring Bridge and Tangle Wire while also pumping up the team with Chief of the Foundry and Steel Overseer. With cards like Urza, Lord High Artificer and Tezzeret the Seeker, the deck can generate a lot of mana to cast powerful spells like The Antiquities War and Transmute Artifact. In addition, the deck includes disruptive spells like Force of Will and Spellskite to protect the game plan and ensure victory through a mix of aggro and control strategies.
